Sparking Anvil Avenue~
   This large, perfectly fitted cobblestone avenue stretches as far north as
the eye can see.  Breaking the perfection of the cobblestones are two ruts, set
in the middle of the avenue.  They certainly look odd, placed amid the
perfectly set cobblestones, and may warrant additional attention from the
curious.  This particular section of the road is quite busy, and is filled with
a variety of people, from dwarf and human to kender and gnome.  Wagons seem to
be constantly rolling in and out of the gate, the ones entering either
continuing northward or pulling into the wagonyard to the west.  To the east
lies a squat wooden building, from which the sounds of revelry can be heard.  
A wooden sign hangs above its door.    
