A Large Courtyard~
   This is a large courtyard made of neatly fitted, smooth flagstones.  The
courtyard is rectangular in shape, and tall stone walls of dwarven
craftsmanship surround it to the west and south.  The Warrior's Guild uses this
courtyard as a practice yard, sparring with eachother, as well as testing
initiates.  In the center of the courtyard, the floor sinks into a rectangular
depression, forming a natural 'arena' of sorts.  Simple straw mats sit evenly
spaced around the arena, where observers or warriors may sit and watch the
matches.  Weapon racks sit on either end of the courtyard, holding an
impressive array of weaponry.  The flagstones are swept, and everything in the
courtyard is kept impressively clean.  One thing that catches your eye are
symbols etched into the center of the west and south walls.    
