   Stone Hearth Lane is one of the smaller streets in the settlement of Garnet,
being one of the mainly residential routes here.  The paving stones are of a
decidedly plain design, though still of the very sturdiest quality.  The
dwarven residents of Garnet can occasionally be seen walking the lane here,
coming from the settlement proper or heading out to work or take care of
business.  Now and then a few dwarven children scramble across the lane,
engaged in a furious game of goblin ball or some other sport.    
